{
  "style": "IEEE",
  "texts": [
    "Kumar et al.",
    "recently conducted a study to investigate the potential and existing limitations of AI text-toimage creation in providing images of medical illnesses affecting the face [87].",
    "They demonstrated that AI textto-image synthesis is easily possible for hypothyroidism, a disorder with symmetrical features.",
    "However, in case of Horner syndrome, a disorder with asymmetrical facial features, appropriate images could only be created after some further minor editing, indicating a potential limitation of these tools.",
    "DALL•E 2, an AI-powered text-topicture system, was utilized in a study to generate clinical images for medical and plastic surgery education purposes [88]."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "recently conducted a study to investigate the potential and existing limitations of AI text-toimage creation in providing images of medical illnesses affecting the face [87].",
    "DALL•E 2, an AI-powered text-topicture system, was utilized in a study to generate clinical images for medical and plastic surgery education purposes [88]."
  ]
}